      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "$33,900 - Good overall condition and honestly priced for what it is. This vehicle appears well-kept, shows normal signs of use for its age, and presents nicely inside and out. It runs well, feels solid, and should make a dependable choice for someone looking for a clean used vehicle without expecting a perfect, like-new example.",
