    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition vehicle that shows nicely and should appeal to buyers looking for a solid, presentable car. The exterior has a clean appearance with normal cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect for its age and use, and the interior is in good shape overall with typical signs of use but nothing out of the ordinary. It appears to have been cared for and should make a dependable, attractive option for someone who wants a nice vehicle without paying mint-condition money.",
