    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Straightforward, budget-friendly transportation with solid value for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for an affordable project, basic runabout, or cost-conscious option with upside. Priced to reflect its condition and presented with transparency, it\u2019s a practical opportunity for buyers who know what they\u2019re looking for.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect and it shows its age, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option for someone who wants simple transport without spending a fortune. Great as a first car, a project, or a handy spare to have around. Priced fairly for what it is, and sold by someone who believes in being straight with buyers \u2014 come have a look and see if it suits what you need.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with strong mechanical potential. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels composed enough to be a practical daily, weekend beater, or build base. It\u2019s not a showroom car and shows its age cosmetically, but that also means you\u2019re getting an honest, usable car with plenty of life left for someone who appreciates simple, serviceable hardware. Great option for a buyer who wants dependable core components without paying premium money.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Used and rough, but ready for someone who needs basic transportation without the big bill. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Built with the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake, this car is a budget-friendly opportunity for someone who appreciates potential over polish. It has the seasoned presence of a vehicle that\u2019s seen life and still stands ready for its next chapter\u2014whether that\u2019s a practical around-town runner, a hands-on project, or a useful backup to keep in the driveway. If you like machines with personality and the chance to make something your own, this one has a story left to tell.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Reliable transportation at a budget-friendly price, this vehicle is a straightforward value for the right buyer. It shows its age and would benefit from some cosmetic and mechanical attention, but it remains an affordable option for commuting, errands, or a project-minded owner looking to get into a vehicle without overspending. Priced to reflect condition and deliver strong value.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
